Fast decision tree

Use this to pick the bucket quickly.

If it is…
	•	array/string scan → Strip
	•	hashing/count memory → Lookup-table
	•	matrix/maze/board → Grid
	•	tree/list/trie → Node-link
	•	heights/intervals/geometry → Coordinate plane
	•	stack/queue/heap → Container
	•	SQL/pandas rows → Relational table
	•	DP/memo recurrence → State table
	•	math/carry/xor/parity → Formula board
	•	bitmask/range tree/jump table → Range/bit-state
	•	general graph/state machine → Graph network
	•	design/internal process → Object/process

