The visual canvas itself is a heuristic.

Choose based on state:
	•	strip/timeline → array, window, pointers
	•	lookup table → hashing/counting
	•	grid/board → matrix BFS/DFS/2D DP
	•	node-link → lists, trees, tries
	•	chart/interval line → geometry, heights, intervals
	•	container → stack/queue/heap
	•	state table → DP
	•	formula board → math/invariant
	•	graph network → graph/state machine
	•	object/process box → design/API/buffer problems

Heuristic:
choose the drawing that makes the invariant visible.

⸻

