11) Where to place it relative to the main drawing

Best default

Right side panel.

Better if the invariant is central

Put the invariant immediately beside the active state.

Better if assumptions are structural

Attach them directly to the input.
Examples:
	•	“Sorted” above array
	•	“DAG” above graph
	•	“Unweighted” on edges
	•	“Lowercase only” above string

Better if edge cases are high risk

