13) Standard icon set

Use simple symbols repeatedly.

✓ Check mark
	•	valid
	•	settled
	•	invariant satisfied
	•	accepted result

✗ Cross
	•	invalid
	•	rejected
	•	popped
	•	discarded

! Warning
	•	edge case
	•	assumption-sensitive area
	•	overflow risk
	•	weighted edges / duplicates / null possibility

★ Star
	•	answer update
	•	key turning point
	•	canonical state
	•	important invariant

? Question
	•	candidate under test
	•	feasibility check
	•	branch decision

∞
	•	unreachable / uninitialized distance

Ø or ∅
	•	empty
	•	null
	•	no value
	•	empty set/list/queue

… Ellipsis
	•	omitted repeated structure
